c: 22
v: 36
t: "E gelooЙ—i [fayЙ—i] Й—in Men waЙ—anii on Й—i jeyaaЙ—um e Maandeeji Alla no woodani on e majji moЖҙЖҙere, jaЕӢtee Innde Alla e dow majji ko Й—i saffiniiЙ—i si becce majji Й—en yanii haray Гұaamee immorde e majji Гұamminon kadi yonndiniiЙ—o e weeЙ“itotooЙ—o, ko wano nii, Men eltirani on Й—i belajo'o onon on jarnay"